VoIP Business Click2Call Extension: 

VoIP Business Click2Call extension- Call any number on your web pages with a single click.

This extension makes displayed numbers on your web browser clickable. While surfing the internet, you can click on any number to call through your VoIP Business dialer. 
Benefits of VoIP Business Click2Call Extension:

Login to your VoIP Business accounts through your extension.
You can select the calling method of your choice. VoIP Business extension provides you with four options:
1. Desktop.
2. Mobile.
3. Tab.
4. SIP

You can choose whether you want Number Overlay or not.
VoIP Business Click2Call extension provides a URL exception where you can choose any domain to deactivate Click2Call.
